00:43:27,047 --> 00:43:28,968
[SPEAKER_07]: Going to Jennifer Sullivan on Zoom.

410
00:43:29,088 --> 00:43:29,728
[SPEAKER_07]: I will unmute you.

411
00:43:30,568 --> 00:43:31,609
[SPEAKER_07]: Oh, someone already did, great.

